title: Abraham Lincoln Birthplace National Historical Park: Field Trips
body: Field Trips      Whether you plan your own visit to the park or want to be part of a ranger led program, a variety of opportunities are available to educational groups visiting the park. Please be aware that ranger led program schedules, facility hours of operation, and ranger availability may impact your planned field trip. To schedule a field trip for your class, please complete and send in the reservation form. Please review the park's field trip policy before scheduling a class field trip to the park. For more information contact the park at (270) 358-3137 or www.nps.gov/abli.     Results  There are no results to show.
